{"tid":849140,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Stan Lee 親口證實！漫威第一位中國女英雄角色：鄧紫棋！","createTime":"2018-10-05T12:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T23:40:26.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3a43d40bccf95d566533407ddd19ec19df9c4c","tid":849140,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/83264/5bb5dd0f6d7d8.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F83264%2F5bb5dd0f6d7d8.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=92eb1b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然《猛毒》( Venom ) 評價褒貶不一，甚至有國外媒體評為「它就像是一部從前 MCU 時代來的作品。」，但頂著漫威（MARVEL）出品的光環，還是讓它穩坐話題冠軍！話說我們能有這麼多經典的英雄電影可以看，不得不歸功於「漫威之父」Stan Lee 了。今年已經 95 歲的他依舊有著一顆年輕人的心，在他筆下創造出鋼鐵人、美國隊長、浩克、雷神索爾....等受到全世界歡迎的英雄角色！這位傳奇英雄教父雖然已經有了崇高地位，但他還有一個願望想完成，那就是創造一位「來自中國的漫威英雄」！如今他的願望似乎即將成真了...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HazVoAAldbw/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FHazVoAAldbw%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=de9a8690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近 Stan Lee 在 IG 分享了一張照片，是鄧紫棋手拿一張漫畫人物海報的合照，並轉分享鄧紫琪的感言：「從未想過有一天我會有機會變成超級英雄！超級無敵興奮！大家覺得我的超能力會是什麼呢？」 原來這位漫畫人物就是 Stan Lee 最新創作出的中國女英雄，而靈感就是來自於鄧紫棋！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/83264/5bb5dce894b26.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F83264%2F5bb5dce894b26.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=b4cc85b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來日前 Stan Lee 因緣際會下與鄧紫棋見面時，就被對方的歌聲深深感動，有報導指出普巴和摩連奴在訓練中出現爭執，這段見面也讓 Stan Lee 有了靈感，決定以鄧紫棋為藍本打造出第一位中國漫威女英雄！Stan Lee 微博全文寫下：「上次他的中國之行，遇上一位很有才華的年輕女孩 GEM 鄧紫棋，她歌聲的力量完全是史丹李創造這位超級英雄的完美藍圖！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/83264/5bb5dcb947212.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F83264%2F5bb5dcb947212.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=50cb8570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據海報上的人名，這位女英雄名稱為 JEWEL，即珠寶之意，一頭褐髮，穿著俐落的緊身戰袍，手上拿著類似光劍的武器，關於 JEWEL 的能力與背景目前尚未公布，有任何最新進展我們也會隨時為大家更新！你期待這位女英雄嗎？"},{"pid":"ef690885a60602d21872fb801c301ffeaabd53a2","tid":849140,"uid":89931,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等睇trump清算marvel"},{"pid":"18b3c6bf397cf9ce4fbf175f3a0635a156672598","tid":849140,"uid":128928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"點解個女英雄望落去識   無胸術   既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f697a8090a98b39a5b8b864936d362d1543f7d","tid":849140,"uid":14423,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"有報導指出普巴和摩連奴在訓練中出現爭執，這段見面也讓 Stan Lee 有了靈感，決定以鄧紫棋為藍本打造出第一位中國漫威女英雄"},{"pid":"ce8e6e56dd71fee3970e0dc32d0e3438de6eae30","tid":849140,"uid":157902,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"張圖畫風似日系漫畫多啲囉，一啲都唔marvel feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要係自大gem，真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7a1eb9694a21b7717644356987d7686b259a3a","tid":849140,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:50:31.000Z","msg":"支持摩佬"},{"pid":"a6ed3db756cc93e567a19323e27f0410bffd6776","tid":849140,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"呀漿應該係宇宙女英雄啦 中國對佢嚟講太細啦"},{"pid":"ed241f5b7a91933be78fa323f72b1975872b8dae","tid":849140,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"明明就揸住兩碌假鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/no